    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that still looks fantastic on the road? This beauty has been my pride and joy, and it\u2019s in really solid shape. It runs like a dream and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s the perfect choice if you want a quality car that\u2019s ready for many more adventures without that 'brand new' price tag. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
