    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example delivers an visceral driving experience through its 6-speed manual gearbox and limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, with critical preventative maintenance addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under load. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the engine's compression is strong and the suspension geometry is dialed for precision. This is a driver-focused machine with excellent mechanical synchronicity and an unfiltered exhaust note.",
      "price": 34500.0,
