      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained driver that still turns heads. The exterior showcases a deep, lustrous finish, with only minor, negligible imperfections that speak to its honest history on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the upholstery is clean and supportive, the electronics function exactly as intended, and the air conditioning blows ice-cold. Mechanically, it is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has benefited from regular, documented oil changes and recent brake service. It has been garage-kept to preserve the trim and seals, ensuring a quiet, rattle-free ride. This is a turn-key example perfect for someone who values both performance and aesthetic appeal.",
