      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with independent throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing direct engagement to the M-variable limited-slip differential. The rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and the suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the drivetrain is exceptionally tight, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience. Recent fluid analysis confirms the health of the internal components, making this a turn-key platform for the discerning enthusiast.",
